        <h1>Skupper Private Network</h1>

        <p>
          Skupper enables components running on multiple sites to communicate
          securely without code or network changes. You create a site, link
          sites and expose components to this network, making them look like
          they are all on the same network.
        </p>

        <p>
          With Skupper, your application components can be located anywhere, in
          cloud providers, data centers, and multiple regions.
        </p>
